::Spears::

Her body jerked as the trainer program finished it's domination of 
her original programs.  Her Maximal program was almost gone 
completely, but a small portion, that which the trainer proram 
couldn't take over, was all that was left.  Her trainer program tried 
to fight the device that kept her in stasis lock.  A small ribbon of 
smoke escaped from the spot where the device was attached to her body.
